#

Double Cheeseburger

25 min
$10
800 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyWheat

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinComfort Food

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

BeefCheeseburgerAmericanQuick Meal

Description

A classic American double cheeseburger loaded with juicy beef patties and melted cheese, served on a soft bun.

Ingredients

  • ground beef: 1 lb
  • cheddar cheese slices: 4
  • burger buns: 2
  • lettuce: 2 leaves
  • tomato: 1, sliced
  • pickles: 4 slices
  • ketchup: 2 tbsp
  • mustard: 1 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
